Treat your dog to a new collar with a personal touch! Have your pet's name embroidered onto these luxe collars in the colour and font of your choice, plus each collar comes with an engraved ID tag.

Designed with technically superior material, the strong nylon webbing finish will see this collar last for years to come whilst the neoprene padding gives absolute comfort around your pet's neck. The ultimate in pet style, safety and practicality!

Additional information and key product features:
Personalised Embroidered Dog Collar – Raspberry Pink.
Comes with a FREE engraved matching ID tag.
Made with neoprene padding and nylon webbing.
Features a stainless steel buckle.

Personalisation information:
Personalised Pets will need the following details:
- The name you would like embroidered onto the collar.
- The colour of the thread you would like (any non-metallic colour).
- The font you would like, can be ANY Microsoft Word font.
- The details you would like engraved onto both sides of the ID tag (12 characters per line).
- The colour of the collar and ID tag you would like. Choose from Blue, Black, Red or Pink.
